export abstract class Display {
    static readonly block = "block"
    static readonly inline_block = "inline-block"
    static readonly inline = "inline"
    static readonly flex = "flex"
    static readonly inline_flex = "inline-flex"
    static readonly table = "table"
    static readonly inline_table = "inline-table"
    static readonly table_caption = "table-caption"
    static readonly table_cell = "table-cell"
    static readonly table_column = "table-column"
    static readonly table_column_group = "table-column-group"
    static readonly table_footer_group = "table-footer-group"
    static readonly table_header_group = "table-header-group"
    static readonly table_row_group = "table-row-group"
    static readonly table_row = "table-row"
    static readonly flow_root = "flow-root"
    static readonly grid = "grid"
    static readonly inline_grid = "inline-grid"
    static readonly contents = "contents"
    static readonly list_item = "list-item"
    static readonly hidden = "hidden"
}
